            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">What's New</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-black mb-4">Last updated: January 22, 2026</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span><strong>Added AI Builder Finder</strong> - Interactive quiz that recommends the right builder based on your answers (5 questions, 30 seconds)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span><strong>Re-tested Durable AI</strong> - Generation speed improved from 45s to 30s. Updated review with new timing data.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span><strong>Added Pineapple Builder review</strong> - Niche restaurant-focused builder tested (28 hours). Score: 7.9/10.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span><strong>CodeDesign.ai re-scored</strong> - Clean code export improved. Score adjusted from 7.8 to 8.2 after re-test.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
