					<!-- TESTING METHODOLOGY DISCLOSURE -->
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-indigo-50 border-[3px] border-purple-300 p-6 md:p-8 my-10 relative overflow-hidden">
						<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-400/10 -mr-16 -mt-16 rounded-full"></div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">How I Tested These Tools</h2>
						<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">Full transparency on my process</p>

						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
							<strong>127+ hours of actual testing.</strong> Not demo sites, not reading feature lists—I built <strong>real websites</strong> across 15+ AI builders and documented what broke.
						</p>

						<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-sm mb-3">WHAT I BUILT</h3>
								<ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
									<li>• 7 portfolio sites (different niches)</li>
									<li>• 4 e-commerce stores (real products)</li>
									<li>• 3 local business sites</li>
									<li>• 2 agency websites</li>
									<li>• 1 blog with 50+ posts</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-sm mb-3">WHAT I MEASURED</h3>
								<ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
									<li>• Generation time (exact seconds)</li>
									<li>• PageSpeed scores (mobile/desktop)</li>
									<li>• Customization depth (1-10 scale)</li>
									<li>• Export code quality</li>
