							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS BOX -->
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-orange-50 border-[3px] border-yellow-400 p-6 md:p-8 my-10 relative overflow-hidden">
						<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-400/10 -mr-16 -mt-16 rounded-full"></div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Unexpected Findings After 127 Hours</h2>
						<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">Things that surprised me</p>

						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<span class="text-yellow-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
								<div>
									<p class="font-black text-gray-900">AI-generated content sounds robotic in EVERY tool</p>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Not just one builder—all of them. The text AI generates is generic, repetitive, and obviously AI-written. <strong>Expect to rewrite 80% of what it produces.</strong></p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<span class="text-yellow-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
								<div>
									<p class="font-black text-gray-900">PageSpeed scores vary wildly (and matter more than you think)</p>
